      "title": "Litro to reduce prices by Rs. 100-200 on Monday (5)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Litro Gas says that it will take steps to reduce the price of a domestic gas cylinder by between Rs. 100 and Rs. 200.",
        "Its Chairman, Muditha Piris mentioned that the price reduction will be implemented from midnight Monday (5).",
        "The Chairman added that the calculations related to the new prices are also being carried out at present.",
        "In the meantime, Laugfs Gas stated that no decision has been taken to lower gas prices."
      ],
